title: Sonatine (Micheline Lanctot, 1984) No subtitles
description:
Another domestic melodrama from Micheline Lanctot, definitely worthwhile for those who appreciate her other work. Pascale Bussieres is also worth seeing - she did a great performance in Ma Vie en Cinemascope. No English subtitles... maybe someone can find some. I have more Lanctot if people show an interest in this one.

PLEASE NOTE: This is NOT the 1993 Japanese movie... you have been warned.
